<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=9944595847490></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9944595847490><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=7&mid=9944595847490>RE: What to do?</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Jul 6th 6:46 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>As a high elf cleric I had weight problems also. A good item to get is the silver ruby veil. It's a wisdom item and has 4 str as well. In addition its not too awfully expensive (around 200pp). Of course, you will still have weight problems but they wont be as bad.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
