<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=9941130074706></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9941130074706><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=7&mid=9941130074706>RE: is this good solo class?</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?id=33184><span id= >Brakiss</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>6 posts</td></tr>
