	   <tr><td colspan=2>Organize by function then set hot keys to open the section you want.<br> I put all my "always up" spells on pages 1 and 2, the key key "/book 1" is labled main.<br><br>  All by buffs go starting at about page 10 so that hot key is called buffs and is "/book 10"<br><br>  Utility spells go all the way in the back and this is where i put Gate, bind, summon food/water all the ods and ends you may need but don't use often.  I'm debating with myself about pulling out all the DD spells and making a section for them too.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
